node.text: Happy 2nd Birthday baby! I can’t believe you’re already 2 I wish you would slow down a little! Me and your father love you soooo much and are so so proud of you! This past year you took your first steps and are now saying full sentences. What amazes me the most about you is your kind heart and how you say hi to everyone you meet. You also hug and kiss the other kids at daycare when they cry because they miss their parents. How are you so brave already!? I just want you to know that I love you more then myself and am so grateful to be your mother!😭🙏🏽💗
